header.gameNote: HALL OF FAME CLASSIC POWERED BY SHOTTRACKER

videos.description: Stanford's Bryce Wills drives and takes on two Butler defenders in the paint, finishing at the rim for the basket and the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Wills scores through contact for Stanford and-1 bucket) 2019/11/26

videos.headline: Wills scores through contact for Stanford and-1 bucket

videos.description: Stanford guard Tyrell Terry pulls up from deep and buries a 3-pointer as the halftime buzzer sounds to tie the game at 29.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Stanford's Terry ties game with buzzer-beating triple) 2019/11/26

videos.headline: Stanford's Terry ties game with buzzer-beating triple

videos.description: Sean McDermott takes an awkward step in transition and goes down in pain.  He'd have to be helped off the court and wheeled to the locker room.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Butler's McDermott exits with lower leg injury) 2019/11/26

videos.headline: Butler's McDermott exits with lower leg injury

videos.description: After Bryce Wills puts Stanford ahead with a powerful slam, Kamar Baldwin hits a go-ahead jumper to put Butler ahead for good.
